title: Jaguars Top Pick, Interesting Draft Players, Packers Needs, Broncos Questions, and Prospect Ickey Okwonu
itunes:title: Jaguars Top Pick, Interesting Draft Players, Packers Needs, Broncos Questions, and Prospect Ickey Okwonu
description:
This edition of The Good Morning Football Podcast begins with the Jaguars options with the top pick in the NFL Draft.  Hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Super Bowl Champion Michael Robinson debate if there is a clear cut #1 player to be taken. Sticking with the Draft, Peter lists his most interesting 'players' as teams prepare for the Draft.  The Packers need to make some moves and the table explores what needs to be done.  Moving to the AFC, the table asks if the Broncos are the biggest question mark in the crowded Conference.  We wrap up with a conversation with Draft Prospect Ickey Okwonu, who reveals his preparations to play in the NFL.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
